    CR -->|manages| LLMBatchGWStatus
    CR -->|manages| LLMBatchGWFinalizers
    CR -->|manages| Certificates
    CR -->|manages| HTTPRoutes
    CR -->|watches| RefGrants
    CR -->|manages| SvcMonitors
    CR -->|manages| PodMonitors
    CR -->|manages| PromRules

    %% Leader election
    LeaderRole -->|manages| Leases
    LeaderRole -->|manages| LeaderEvents

    %% Aggregate roles (user-facing)
    AdminCR -.->|"full CRUD"| LLMBatchGW
    ViewCR -.->|"read-only"| LLMBatchGW

